cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY. 

This paper focuses on developing a robot system for self-supervised learning of 6D object pose estimation, which is a core task in robot manipulation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also heavily relies on computer vision techniques for object segmentation and pose estimation, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of deep learning models for self-supervised learning and data augmentation indicates that it could also fit into cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the interaction between the robot and the environment, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
